<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="move-on">move on</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>继续前进；转换 (话题)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>After a few minutes, the bus moved on again.
几分钟后，公共汽车又继续往前开了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I think we’ve talked enough about that subject; let’s move on. 
我认为这个话题我们已经谈得够多了，咱们换个话题吧。</p></div></div>